reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cut but not sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Needs a little help to stay on but it’s super cute and my baby loves it. ( 2 months ) maybe just zip tie it or something. I also thought it had music because of the picture, but it’s just one of the toys that had a little bell in it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for in the car
reviews.reviewText: No surprises with this product. Easy to attach with clip and adjust the length. I have it at the highest setting in the photo since my girl will look at things but not touch them yet. It doesn’t make noise if the baby isn’t hitting it so you don’t have to worry about it being too distracting to the driver. We bought this after my girl consistently got bored and fussy in the car. Seems to help so far.
